<HEADLINE> Gunmen's Parents Target of Suit </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	DENVER (AP) -- An attorney for relatives of a student slain at  
Columbine High School plans to file a $250 million lawsuit against 
the parents of student gunmen Dylan Klebold and Eric Harris. 
</P>
