	An attorney representing Wayne and Katherine Harris, Eric's  
parents, did not return a telephone message seeking comment 
Wednesday. Lisa Simon, a spokeswoman for the law firm that 
represents Thomas and Susan Klebold, Dylan's parents, declined to 
comment. 
</P>
<P>
