	Nine minutes into the second half, Anders Limpar sent in a  
corner kick. Clash defender Jamie Clark headed the ball off the leg 
of teammate Wade Barrett to it into the net for an own goal. 
</P>
<P>
	Rapids midfielder Ross Paule scored four minutes later, and Dely  
Valdes provided Colorado's final goal in the 73rd minute with 
assists from Harris and Marcus Hahnemann. 
</P>
<P>
	Midfielder Eddie Lewis earned San Jose's second goal in the 63rd  
minute. 
</P>
